{"thig7.3:0.1":"Therigatha 7.3 ","thig7.3:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","thig7.3:0.3":"Upacalatherigatha ","thig7.3:1.1":"“Satimati cakkhumati, ","thig7.3:1.2":"bhikkhuni bhavitindriya; ","thig7.3:1.3":"Pativijjhi padam santam, ","thig7.3:1.4":"akapurisasevitam”. ","thig7.3:2.1":"“Kim nu jatim na rocesi, ","thig7.3:2.2":"jato kamani bhunjati; ","thig7.3:2.3":"Bhunjahi kamaratiyo, ","thig7.3:2.4":"mahu pacchanutapini”. ","thig7.3:3.1":"“Jatassa maranam hoti, ","thig7.3:3.2":"hatthapadana chedanam; ","thig7.3:3.3":"Vadhabandhapariklesam, ","thig7.3:3.4":"jato dukkham nigacchati. ","thig7.3:4.1":"Atthi sakyakule jato, ","thig7.3:4.2":"sambuddho aparajito; ","thig7.3:4.3":"So me dhammamadesesi, ","thig7.3:4.4":"jatiya samatikkamam. ","thig7.3:5.1":"Dukkham dukkhasamuppadam, ","thig7.3:5.2":"dukkhassa ca atikkamam; ","thig7.3:5.3":"Ariyam catthangikam maggam, ","thig7.3:5.4":"dukkhupasamagaminam. ","thig7.3:6.1":"Tassaham vacanam sutva, ","thig7.3:6.2":"viharim sasane rata; ","thig7.3:6.3":"Tisso vijja anuppatta, ","thig7.3:6.4":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","thig7.3:7.1":"Sabbattha vihata nandi, ","thig7.3:7.2":"tamokhandho padalito; ","thig7.3:7.3":"Evam janahi papima, ","thig7.3:7.4":"nihato tvamasi antaka”. ","thig7.3:8.1":"… Upacala theri …. ","thig7.3:9.1":"Sattakanipato nitthito. "}